{"tid":1381150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[買飛教學]如果你冇人接放學要搭鐵走","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T14:57:11.000Z","uid":93035,"like":70,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c872a048ead1e8656ab7b5e0b8827e8a7f1fa786","tid":1381150,"uid":93035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:28:15.000Z","msg":"我做地鐵嘅朋友冇ac，所以代佢po<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有鑑於近日發夢見到有好多戰友喺地鐵幫人買單程飛走，而佢哋多數都會買比較貴嘅長程飛，所以依家想提供一個啲方法俾大家參考，令籌番黎既錢唔好白白浪費。<br />\n<br />\n1. 買飛只需買前一/後一站即可。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因：慳錢。<br />\n例子：係銅鑼灣站，買灣仔/天后既飛，乘客去到各自嘅目的地先喺客務中心補飛錢。咁就唔需要買又貴又遠嘅飛，而又入到閘。慳番黎既錢留待下一次用。<br />\n注意⚠<br />\n買成人飛，唔好買特惠！<br />\n<br />\n2. 當日用唔完既車飛，可以喺當日收站前(含午夜12點後)退飛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因：慳錢。<br />\n注意⚠<br />\nA. 當日呢兩個字嘅意思係指收站之前，包括午夜12點之後嘅時間。<br />\nB. 必定要當日(地鐵收站前)退票，因為第2日就係廢票。<br />\n<br />\n3. 逼不得已下，可使用普通八達通，但千萬唔好用個人八達通(學生/有名)。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因：方便，無個人資料。<br />\n例子：普通八達通，唔會有個人資料，地鐵查唔到。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總之，買成人單程（1個站），到目的地去客務中心補錢係最好。</span></span><br />\n<br />\nfrom小小狗鐵職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7d12f38bbc68e446712c491be38003fbf6c781","tid":1381150,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:28:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［重開 長文慎屌］727 728 賽後檢討<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380962</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ebeff04076dcfc47bc9cb5ab2e7d34b23ba0d3b2","tid":1381150,"uid":93035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"一1"},{"pid":"291db92a715874541380128e912874479b6aa070","tid":1381150,"uid":93035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:29:16.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"83acf211d1ce186f107ba00d7c12a3ffd5fec4b9","tid":1381150,"uid":93035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:29:26.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"4e855113c402e11d5f9d819acb9abed31cdd8b95","tid":1381150,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:29:29.000Z","msg":"講得出買飛既, 近幾次一定係冇出過去"},{"pid":"1aa4298042ce034ff9243481916b0a380c5a5e40","tid":1381150,"uid":93035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"唔好石沉大海<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a7d21de4177ae885e9d1d55815e8c06b4a3143","tid":1381150,"uid":276440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:31:07.000Z","msg":"去補錢會唔會有d風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8418292eec2c13ad2c14f89a4b77b46b1b795a98","tid":1381150,"uid":53736,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"4e855113c402e11d5f9d819acb9abed31cdd8b95","tid":1381150,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:29:29.000Z","msg":"講得出買飛既, 近幾次一定係冇出過去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"直接跳閘算鳩數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4cc2f5ed8b3e18a39f7d768f3d276d00c1c659","tid":1381150,"uid":184500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8418292eec2c13ad2c14f89a4b77b46b1b795a98","tid":1381150,"uid":53736,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"4e855113c402e11d5f9d819acb9abed31cdd8b95","tid":1381150,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:29:29.000Z","msg":"講得出買飛既, 近幾次一定係冇出過去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"直接跳閘算鳩數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:32:45.000Z","msg":"正想講"},{"pid":"d0e3e3a0